Package admin

Class Database.RowData

  • java.lang.Object
    • admin.Database.RowData
  • Enclosing class:
    Database
    public static class Database.RowData
extends Object
    In the context of the database, RowData represents the data we'd see in a row. We make RowData a static class of Database because it is only an abstract representation of a row of the database. RowData and Database are connected: Both gets updated if one changes.
